      "content": "but those distractions dont actually change anything. they're just ways to distract ourselves from the fact that we're suffering for no reason. why is it more \"meaningful\" to struggle through all this pain just to reach an inevitable end? it feels like we're just prolonging the inevitable for the sake of a lie.",
